13 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 12 O.S. 2021, Section 1764, is
14 amended to read as follows:
15 Section 1764. A fee of Forty-five Dollars ($45.00) Eighty-five
16 Dollars ($85.00) shall be charged and collected for the filing of
17 the affidavit for the commencement of any action for an amount of
18 Five Thousand Dollars ($5,000.00) or less. Any action in excess of
19 Five Thousand Dollars ($5,000.00) shall be subject to the filing
20 fees provided in Title 28 of the Oklahoma Statutes for the same kind
21 of action as filed in district court. For the filing of any
22 counterclaim or setoff, fees shall be charged and collected pursuant
23 to Section 152.1 of Title 28 of the Oklahoma Statutes. Except as
24 otherwise provided in Section 1772 of this title, no other fee or
