11 collect only such fees and charges as are allowed by law for like
12 services in other actions. All fees collected as authorized by this
13 section and Section 1772 of this title shall be deposited with other
14 fees that are collected by the district court. Any statute
15 providing for an award of attorney fees shall be applicable to the
16 small claims division if the attorney makes an appearance in the
17 case, whether before or after judgment or on hearing for disclosure
18 of assets.
19 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
